---
const metadata = {
  alt: "Gabe Newell",
  src: "/gabe.webp",
};
---

<section
  class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-16 xl:gap-18 w-full mb-12 md:mb-16 lg:mb-24"
  aria-label="Frase de Gabe Newell"
>
  <!-- Image -->
  <div
    class="w-48 md:w-64 lg:w-80 xl:w-96 aspect-[3/4] flex-shrink-0"
  >
    <img
      src={metadata.src}
      alt={metadata.alt}
      class="rounded-[15px] w-full h-full object-cover shadow-lg"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Quote -->
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 w-full md:flex-1">
    <blockquote class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-7">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-7">
        <p class="italic font-light text-lg md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl leading-relaxed md:leading-relaxed lg:leading-relaxed text-center md:text-left">
          La clave del éxito es admitir que no sabes algo y luego descubrir cómo
          aprenderlo
        </p>
        <footer class="italic font-light text-base md:text-xl lg:text-2xl xl:text-3xl text-center md:text-left opacity-80">
          <cite>- Gabe Newell</cite>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>
